    | in Appointment einschreiben (Studenten) | ! post appointment_request/set body:{appointment_id}, {time}, {user_id}...   |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Appointment annehmen/ablehnen           | ! put appointment_request/{id} body:{state}                                  |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! post appointment_request/ban_user body:{user_id}                           |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Appointment erstellen                   | ! post appointment/set body:{docent_id}, {day}, {time}, {description}        |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Appointment l√∂schen                     | ! delete appointment/{appointment_id}                                        |
